// ── I1: Cross-Integration Tests Batch 4 (Final — remaining 20 primitives) ──
//
// Covers: persona, context, flow, anchor, tool, memory, type, agent, lambda,
// daemon, know, believe, speculate, doubt, step, reason, validate, use,
